                <text type="warning_situation">
				<p>MINOR FLOODING LIKELY AT WOODSIDE THURSDAY AFTERNOON</p>
<p>MINOR FLOODING OCCURRING AT OAKBANK </p>

				<p/>
				<p>Moderate rainfall totals have been observed over the Onkaparinga River catchment over the last few days, causing river and creek level rises.</p>
<p>Further rainfall is forecast for the remainder of Thursday into Friday, which is likely to cause minor flooding along the upper Onkaparinga River at Woodside. Oakbank is likely to remain above the minor flood level during Thursday into Friday.</p>

				<p/>

                </text>
                <element type="severity">Minor</element>
